definition: Suichang county in Lishui 麗水|丽水[Li2 shui3], Zhejiang

sentences.english: In 1992~1993, introduction and forestation of Taiwania were made in Suichang County of Zhejiang Province.
sentences.chinese: 年在浙江省遂昌縣對二樹種進行了引種造林試驗。

sentences.english: The Suichang County police couldn't be reached for comment.
sentences.chinese: 目前沒有辦法向遂昌縣公安局聯絡徵求意見。
